snippet.title: Rocket League Sideswipe Season 5 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Sideswipe Season 5 Gameplay Trailer!
Learn more here http://sideswipe.rocketleague.com/news/boost-to-the-future-in-rocket-league-sideswipe-s-futuristic-season-5/

Welcome to the future, where tomorrow is today! Season 5 launches a futuristic Rocket Pass packed with highly experimental Items like the Chikara G1 Car and Holo Data Goal Explosion.

Raise your supply of XP and SP by completing high-tech challenges, or get a blast from the past with 2v2 Volleyball’s grand return to Ranked. 

 The future arrives September 7!

#RocketLeagueSideswipe #SideswipeSeason5 #RLSSeason5
